- "a specific list" refers to a predefined list of actor IDs; 
- "known director" means the movie has a valid director ID; 
- "IMDb link" refers to the link to the movie's IMDb page.

- The specific filmmaker is identified by a unique director_id of 1; 
- IMDb score is a measure of user ratings, with higher scores indicating better user reception; 
- Average user rating is calculated by aggregating the IMDb scores of all movies by the same director.

